,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"碎料啦， 共產主義傳入先史上最鑊"},{"pid":"7b7f2a99d970eceebe55e5fca58b62b18f0d01d5","tid":800062,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"韓國遊客從瀋陽攜血腸、餃子回國 食物被驗出有非洲豬瘟病毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/797866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/797866</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3b144c29272f6e7ec30609564213b95858952ac","tid":800062,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:00:50.000Z","msg":"這就是中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}